race.description: Ladbrokes Quick Multi Qtis 3yo Maiden Handicap
race.comment: ARTISTIC ENDEAVOUR (1) has placed four of his past five starts and looks to be on the doorstep of a maiden victory. Gets a stack of weight relief with the 3kg claim and maps ideally for this from gate four. Rates the testing material. WEEKEND SPIRIT (11) will be ready to peak now third run back from a spell and must be respected out of the Bruce barn. Looms as the main danger. KATIE AINE (7) hit the frame here last time out and the step-up to the mile journey should suit. In the mix. LITTLE MISS CLASSY (10) has been about the money is all four runs this campaign and may trouble the judge with any luck in running.
